fields.name: Parameters
fields.description:
-I <number of trees>
  Number of trees to build.
  (default 100)
 -K <number of features>
  Number of features to consider (<1=int(log_2(#predictors)+1)).
  (default 0)
 -S
  Seed for random number generator.
  (default 1)
 -depth <num>
  The maximum depth of the trees, 0 for unlimited.
  (default 0)
 -O
  Don't calculate the out of bag error.
 -print
  Print the individual trees in the output
 -B
  Break ties randomly when several attributes look equally good.
 -output-debug-info
  If set, classifier is run in debug mode and
  may output additional info to the console
 -do-not-check-capabilities
  If set, classifier capabilities are not checked before classifier is built
  (use with caution).
 -num-decimal-places
  The number of decimal places for the output of numbers in the model (default 2).
